1
00:00:01,990 --> 00:00:09,060
前情提要

2
00:00:02,670 --> 00:00:06,530
人们一直问东问西的  我根本不知道答案
They people keep asking me questions I don't know the answer to.

3
00:00:06,530 --> 00:00:09,620
现在手握机枪的是我们
It's us that have the machine guns now

4
00:00:09,630 --> 00:00:11,710
焦头烂额的是他们
and it's them that's in the mud.

5
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:15,800
枪支  谢尔比先生  我们愿意出大价钱
Guns, Mr Shelby. We'd pay good money.

6
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:16,760
你们是代表谁在谈
For who do you speak?

7
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:19,070
爱尔兰共和军
The Irish Republican Army.

8
00:00:21,180 --> 00:00:23,620
你是什么人  警察吗
What are you? A copper?

9
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:27,820
你因为他是爱尔兰共和军才跟踪他
You went after him because he was IRA.

10
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:30,500
我跟着他是因为我以为他身上有情报
I followed him because I thought he might have information.

11
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,630
卧底最难的一点就是
The difficulty with undercover work,

12
00:00:33,630 --> 00:00:36,710
时刻谨记自己是谁  格蕾丝
Grace, is to remember what you are.

13
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,650
你妹妹在里面生孩子
Your sister's in there giving birth.

14
00:00:39,650 --> 00:00:41,100
有个男人该待在这里
There's one man who should be here.

15
00:00:41,100 --> 00:00:42,960
你说的对  波莉  我发誓
You are right, Poll. On my oath.

16
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,290
告诉弗莱迪来这里没事
Tell Freddie it's safe.

17
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:47,870
欢迎来到这个世界  儿子
Welcome to the world, son.

18
00:00:48,620 --> 00:00:49,620
弗莱迪
Freddie?

19
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:52,420
波莉
Pol!

20
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,410
但警察把他的父亲抓走了
The police came and took his father away!

21
00:00:55,770 --> 00:00:56,840
你个骗子
You liar!

22
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:52,020
丹尼尔·欧文

23
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:05,100
浴   血

24
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:05,100
黑   帮

25
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:05,100
第一季   『人人影视英剧社倾情奉献』   第五集

26
00:02:27,770 --> 00:02:28,900
开门吧  亲爱的
Open up, love.

27
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:31,970
我给你和孩子带了点东西来
I brought more things for you and the baby.

28
00:02:31,970 --> 00:02:33,630
我带了新鲜鸡蛋和面包
I've got some fresh eggs and bread...

29
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:35,590
我把东西放在门口
I'll leave it here.

30
00:02:37,550 --> 00:02:40,080
艾达  多替孩子想想
Ada, think of the little one.

31
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:43,740
孩子可没有原则
Babies don't have principles.

32
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:13,420
你跟她说话了吗
Did you speak to her?

33
00:03:15,130 --> 00:03:16,390
她没有回应
She didn't speak back.

34
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,020
你告诉她了吗
Well, did you tell her?

35
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:25,380
我只会告诉她我确定的真相
I'll only tell her what I know to be true.

36
00:03:27,970 --> 00:03:29,780
我最后再说一遍
It's the last time I am going to say this.

37
00:03:30,340 --> 00:03:33,640
出卖弗莱迪·索恩的人不是我
It wasn't me who shopped Freddie Thorne.

38
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:36,490
汤米
Tommy...

39
00:03:37,170 --> 00:03:38,990
我让你对着圣经发誓
I'd ask you to swear on the Bible,

40
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:41,330
但你做不到  对吗
but you can't swear on that, can you?

41
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:44,060
你对任何东西都毫无敬畏
Nothing you hold is sacred.

42
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,630
我泡了茶
There's tea.

43
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:03,080
新的运作体系
The new system...

44
00:04:04,100 --> 00:04:05,970
所有事都记在日记里  对吗
..everything in the diary, eh?

45
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:14,580
一颗黑星  这是什么意思
A black star? What does that mean?

46
00:04:15,390 --> 00:04:16,740
标上黑星那天
The black star day...

47
00:04:17,550 --> 00:04:20,100
是我们除掉比利·肯波和他的手下的日子
..is the day we take out Billy Kimber and his men.

48
00:04:21,350 --> 00:04:22,680
没人知道这事
No-one knows this!

49
00:04:23,810 --> 00:04:25,200
你的家人都不知道吗
Not even your family?

50
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:27,810
格蕾丝
Grace...

51
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:32,960
我的所有家人都讨厌我
..everyone in my family hates me.

52
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:34,970
我为何还要告诉他们
Why would I tell them?

53
00:04:37,990 --> 00:04:40,410
他彻底失控了  就是这么回事
He's off the bloody rails, is what he is.

54
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:42,640
如果他背叛自己最好的兄弟
If he'll turn nose on his best mate...

55
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:45,720
该死的邻居们  约翰  背后打小报告
Bloody neighbours, John. Snitch behind the curtain.

56
00:04:45,750 --> 00:04:48,910
如果你这么想  那恐怕世上只有你一个人如此
If you think that, you're the only one who does.

57
00:04:49,660 --> 00:04:53,260
看看这个  看看  生意很红火啊
Look at this, look. Bloody raking it in.

58
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:54,590
谁在管理这个马戏团
Who's running this carny?

59
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,700
一个叫马斯顿的人
Name of Marston.

60
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:58,070
准备利用这个拳击场在小希斯度过寒冬
Intends on wintering in Smallheath with this ring.

61
00:04:58,070 --> 00:04:59,710
-是嘛  -难道他没听说过
- Does he! - Ain't he heard

62
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:02,280
要想在小希斯落脚
nobody in Smallheath craps in a pot

63
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:05,020
必须经过汤米大神同意吗
without the decree of Tommy Almighty?

64
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:08,770
马斯顿先生  对吧  拳击场的老板
Mr. Marston, I believe? The ringmaster?

65
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:09,910
我骄傲地回答  正是在下
Proud I am to say so.

66
00:05:09,910 --> 00:05:12,450
很好  那先来文明地谈谈
Yes, well, these here are civilised parts.

67
00:05:13,010 --> 00:05:16,370
想要在这里做让人互相打架的生意
Man wants to set his stall up with fellas lamping each other,

68
00:05:16,370 --> 00:05:18,370
你得先拿到许可证
he needs himself a licence.

69
00:05:18,370 --> 00:05:19,510
许可证
A licence.

70
00:05:20,670 --> 00:05:24,390
交钱才能拿  给管事的人
For a fee. From those in charge.

71
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:26,860
我看不如这样吧
I'll tell you what.

72
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:28,800
我留着我赚到的钱
How about I keep my money,

73
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,810
你把你的许可证塞回自己的屁眼里
and you shove a licence up your arsecrack?

74
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:32,670
你最好别这么跟我说话
You don't want to speak to me like that.

75
00:05:32,670 --> 00:05:34,220
你他妈以为自己是谁啊
And who the bloody hell do you think you are?

76
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:37,710
我叫亚瑟·谢尔比
My name is Arthur Shelby.

77
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:40,180
爸爸
Dad?

78
00:05:46,900 --> 00:05:48,180
天啊
Jesus.

79
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:55,080
谢谢  真是个乖孩子
Thank you. You are a good boy.

80
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:58,980
多谢您  上帝
Bless you, Father,

81
00:05:58,980 --> 00:06:00,650
感谢你赐予我们食物
for these bounties we are about to receive...

82
00:06:00,650 --> 00:06:02,540
老天啊
Jesus Christ...

83
00:06:02,540 --> 00:06:03,970
拜托  女人
Please, woman...

84
00:06:04,660 --> 00:06:05,810
不要渎神
..not in vain.

85
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,600
吃完你的三明治就赶紧走人
Finish your sandwich and sling your hook.

86
00:06:10,190 --> 00:06:11,450
波莉安娜
Pollyanna.

87
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:14,050
我是一家之主的客人
I'm the guest of the head of this family,

88
00:06:14,050 --> 00:06:15,250
你就让我好好做客
so why don't you let me

89
00:06:15,250 --> 00:06:17,320
自己去熨熨衣服买买菜吧
tend to your mangle or your scuttle?

90
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:19,120
一家之主没在家
The head of the family ain't here.

91
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:28,340
汤米  他有时帮我管理生意
Tommy... he sometimes helps me with business.

92
00:06:31,550 --> 00:06:33,840
说曹操曹操到
Well. Speak of the devil.

93
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,740
你好吗  儿子
How are you, son?

94
00:06:38,770 --> 00:06:39,780
滚出去
Get out.

95
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:44,360
好啦  儿子  我已经洗心革面了
Come on, son. I'm a changed man.

96
00:06:45,340 --> 00:06:48,050
这个家十年前需要你的时候
This family needed you ten years ago

97
00:06:48,050 --> 00:06:50,200
你头也不回地走了
when you walked out on this.

98
00:06:50,780 --> 00:06:53,410
现在不欢迎你  滚出这个家
Not now. Get out of this house.

99
00:06:53,500 --> 00:06:54,840
汤米  他已经改过了
Tommy, he's different...

100
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:55,930
你闭嘴
You shut up.

101
00:06:58,910 --> 00:06:59,960
没事的  儿子
It's all right, son.

102
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:06,150
亚瑟·谢尔比不会待在不被欢迎的地方
Arthur Shelby never stays where he is not welcome.

103
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,630
你现在真是个人物了
Quite something you've become.

104
00:07:19,690 --> 00:07:20,550
再见  儿子
Bye, son.

105
00:07:32,090 --> 00:07:33,150
他是我们的爸爸
He's our dad.

106
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:37,890
他是个自私的混蛋
He's a selfish bastard.

107
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:42,030
你说别人是自私的混蛋
You calling someone a selfish bastard?

108
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:45,150
有点可笑吧  汤米
That's a bit rich, Tommy.

109
00:07:45,570 --> 00:07:46,840
都是因为你
I mean, thanks to you...

110
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:50,490
我们已经失去一个妹妹了
..we're already down a bloody sister.

111
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:52,940
你想要见他  亚瑟
If you want to see him, Arthur?

112
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:56,920
你想要见他  那你跟他一起走
You want to see him? You can go with him.

113
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,380
格蕾丝
Grace...

114
00:08:28,150 --> 00:08:31,090
我拿五镑的零钱  行吗
I am taking five pounds from petty cash all right?

115
00:08:31,130 --> 00:08:32,760
那里的零钱不够五镑
We don't have five pounds in petty cash.

116
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,780
那我就有多少拿多少
Then I'll take what we've got.

117
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,830
数一下有多少  留个收据
Count it and leave a receipt.

118
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:41,840
亚瑟  有些账目我不太明白
Arthur, there are some things in the books that I don't understand.

119
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:45,360
-我也一样  -我们每周都给伦敦一个叫
- Likewise. - Every week we pay one pound and ten shillings

120
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:49,690
丹尼尔·欧文的人汇一英镑十先令过去
by postal order to a "Daniel Owen" In London.

121
00:08:49,690 --> 00:08:51,030
高速炮弹丹尼
Danny Whizz Bang,

122
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:54,150
帮我们在卡姆登镇码头的酒吧里探听消息
hangs round the pubs in Camden Town Wharf for us.

123
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:56,070
他耳听八方
He keeps his ears open for business.

124
00:08:56,070 --> 00:08:57,230
是个好人
He's a good man.

125
00:08:57,310 --> 00:08:58,790
高速炮弹丹尼不是死了吗
I thought Danny Whizz Bang was dead.

126
00:08:58,790 --> 00:09:00,720
那你就错了
Then you thought wrong, didn't you?

127
00:09:00,930 --> 00:09:03,120
但我见过他的坟墓  他中枪而死
But I've seen his grave. He was shot.

128
00:09:03,660 --> 00:09:06,360
那是演给意大利人看的
That was a show to satisfy the wops.

129
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:09,220
汤米开枪射出的是羊脑
Tommy just shot some sheep's brains at him.

130
00:09:10,330 --> 00:09:11,690
那墓里葬的是谁
Who is buried in his grave?

131
00:09:16,530 --> 00:09:20,440
格蕾丝  你要是明白事理的话
Now look, Grace, if you know what's good for you,

132
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:23,840
就别问与你无关的问题
you don't ask questions about things that don't concern you.

133
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:26,000
永远别问
Never. Right!

134
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,440
这钱给你
And that's for you.

135
00:09:28,650 --> 00:09:30,550
别告诉汤米我拿了这些钱
And don't tell Tommy I took this.

136
00:10:00,550 --> 00:10:02,700
要我说的话  那孩子需要个藏身之所
The boy needs a good hiding, if you ask me.

137
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:05,050
波莉阿姨也算能保护他吧
Yeah, well, Aunt Polly's close to giving him one.

138
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:07,650
貌似还有约翰和艾达
John and Ada too, it sounds like.

139
00:10:07,650 --> 00:10:10,160
约翰整天都在抱怨规矩
John moans on bloody principle -

140
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:11,910
但要是你见过他的夫人...
but if you saw his Mrs...

141
00:10:15,050 --> 00:10:16,620
你有女人了吗  儿子
You have a girl yourself, son?

142
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:22,080
得让汤米满意  是吗
P'raps when it suits Tommy, eh?

143
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:29,020
战后他整个人都变了
Yeah, well... He's been different, you know, since the war.

144
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:32,620
是啊  战争会改变一个人
Yeah, well... The war can change a man.

145
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,220
我是在说我自己
Speaking for myself, anyway.

146
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:36,760
你在哪打过仗  爸爸
Where did you fight, Dad?

147
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:40,380
到处都打过  儿子
All over, son, all over.

148
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:42,030
是啊  到处
Yeah, all over.

149
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:47,210
接着耶稣拯救了我
Then the salvation of Jesus Christ spread his light over me,

150
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:52,280
我作为朝圣者  去了新世界
and, as a pilgrim, I come to visit the New World...

151
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,620
美国
America.

152
00:10:54,130 --> 00:10:56,730
在那里  我见到了未来
Where I beheld the future.

153
00:10:58,940 --> 00:11:01,970
赌场简直是金钱工厂  儿子
Casinos! Money factories, son.

154
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:05,450
我一直在研究赌场
Look, I've been studying the competition,

155
00:11:07,170 --> 00:11:10,110
他们的骗局和运营系统
their schemes, their systems.

156
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:12,400
-看啊  都在这里  -让我看看
- Look at that... It's all there. - Show me.

157
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:15,350
那行业简直是暴利
There's a fortune to be made here.

158
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:20,370
我已年老体衰  我的心脏就是个破旧的容器
I'm an old man, and my heart's a battered vessel.

159
00:11:20,370 --> 00:11:26,560
但里面  仍搏动着梦想
But within...There still beats the fluttering pulse of a dream...

160
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:32,340
谢尔比赌场和酒店
The Shelby Casino and Hotel...

161
00:11:32,930 --> 00:11:36,930
全世界的人都会蜂拥而来
Gents and dames will come flocking from all corners -

162
00:11:37,170 --> 00:11:40,970
纽约  芝加哥  波士顿
New York, Chicago, Boston -

163
00:11:40,970 --> 00:11:43,890
都会来到谢尔比的地盘  在那里
to The Shelby, where I can stand proudly

164
00:11:43,890 --> 00:11:46,850
我可以与我的孩子们并肩而立
with my dear children by my side.

165
00:11:47,450 --> 00:11:49,290
而里面的女人
And the women there!

166
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:53,000
如新鲜蜜桃一般
Like fresh peaches.

167
00:11:53,260 --> 00:11:54,770
要多少有多少
Thou could have a dozen.

168
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,490
我们都会成为国王
We'd all of us be kings!

169
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:02,160
办赌场要多少钱
How much, how much to get started?

170
00:12:03,090 --> 00:12:05,760
只需一点本钱  就能长成摇钱树
The oak needs but an acorn.

171
00:12:07,570 --> 00:12:08,560
我们干吧
Let's do it.

172
00:12:09,860 --> 00:12:12,020
开干吧
Let's do it. Let's bloody do it.

173
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:13,450
我也非常渴望
It would make my heart beam...

174
00:12:13,450 --> 00:12:17,040
但我不想引起你们兄弟不和
but I don't want to cause any discord between the brothers.

175
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:19,960
不如你先去跟汤米谈谈
So, please, why don't you talk to Tommy first...?

176
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:22,070
我已经受够听他吩咐了
I'm sick of taking orders from him.

177
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:25,970
汤米可不是这个家族仅有的生意脑袋
Tommy's not the only one in the family with a head for business,

178
00:12:27,930 --> 00:12:31,950
谢尔比家族的钱是大家共用的
and Shelby money is Shelby money.

179
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:36,580
感谢上帝给了我这么出色的儿子们
I thank God for my wonderful sons.

180
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:40,630
必须得庆祝一番
This is cause for a celebration!

181
00:12:40,640 --> 00:12:43,860
-干杯  -干杯
