Yes. And do you have a biscuit?

544
00:45:26,690 --> 00:45:28,780
没有  饼干引老鼠
No. They attract mice.

545
00:45:30,310 --> 00:45:32,200
人一回家感觉就不一样了
People look different at home.

546
00:45:32,240 --> 00:45:33,790
怎么不一样
In what way?

547
00:45:34,270 --> 00:45:36,080
卸下警惕
Off guard.

548
00:45:38,940 --> 00:45:40,500
我应该警惕吗
Should I be on my guard?

549
00:45:40,540 --> 00:45:43,810
不用  我只是个喝茶的男人
No, I'm a man who drinks tea.

550
00:45:57,140 --> 00:45:59,770
风声过去后  我就走
When the trouble dies down, I'll go.

551
00:46:06,740 --> 00:46:08,760
你觉得什么时候会过去
When will it die down, do you think?

552
00:46:09,480 --> 00:46:11,400
晚些时候吧
Late, I would say.

553
00:46:14,580 --> 00:46:16,790
那明早之前都不会走了
So, not until the morning then.

554
00:46:18,740 --> 00:46:21,690
是的  明早之前都不会
Yes. I'd say I'll be here till morning.

555
00:46:28,520 --> 00:46:29,650
你有一架留声机
You have a gramophone?

556
00:46:29,710 --> 00:46:30,860
已经坏了
It's broken.

557
00:46:30,920 --> 00:46:32,710
那我们也能跳舞
We could still dance.

558
00:46:37,300 --> 00:46:39,090
是啊  当然
Yes. Why not.

559
00:46:44,370 --> 00:46:46,650
我知道你喜欢正式的邀请
I know you like to be asked properly.

560
00:46:49,040 --> 00:46:51,300
格蕾丝  我能请你跳支舞吗
Grace, can I have this dance?

561
00:49:03,570 --> 00:49:05,250
你还好吗
Are you ok?

562
00:49:05,840 --> 00:49:08,750
我没有听见铲子挖墙的声音
I don't hear the shovels against the wall.

563
00:49:10,610 --> 00:49:12,420
什么铲子
What shovels?

564
00:49:15,910 --> 00:49:17,660
你能帮助我吗
Will you help me?

565
00:49:19,300 --> 00:49:20,700
帮助你什么
Help you with what?

566
00:49:20,750 --> 00:49:22,590
所有的事
With everything...

567
00:49:23,570 --> 00:49:25,800
所有这些操蛋的事
..The whole fucking thing.

568
00:49:25,830 --> 00:49:27,910
操蛋的人生
Fucking life...

569
00:49:28,250 --> 00:49:30,120
生意
..Business.

570
00:49:31,910 --> 00:49:33,670
我找到了你
I've found you.

571
00:49:35,320 --> 00:49:37,190
你也找到了我
And you found me.

572
00:49:39,650 --> 00:49:41,810
我们互相帮助
We'll help each other.

573
00:50:55,870 --> 00:51:00,140
我们在天上的父
Our Father, who art in heaven.

574
00:51:01,130 --> 00:51:03,190
愿人都尊你的名为圣
Hallowed be thy name....

575
00:52:00,760 --> 00:52:03,730
给丘吉尔先生发一封电报
Send a telegram to Mr Churchill...

576
00:52:04,330 --> 00:52:06,820
告诉他我有好消息  很好的消息
I have news, very good news.

577
00:52:08,260 --> 00:52:12,480
告诉他我的工作已经完成
Tell him the business I came to attend to is now complete.

578
00:52:13,090 --> 00:52:15,220
我要离开这里了
I'll be leaving the city.

579
00:52:15,710 --> 00:52:19,980
但在此之前  还有一件事要做
There's just one matter I need to tidy up first.

580
00:53:00,310 --> 00:53:02,050
波莉都告诉你了吧
Polly told you?

581
00:53:17,640 --> 00:53:19,710
你应该选择用枪的
You should have used a gun.

582
00:53:22,000 --> 00:53:24,120
你是在嘲笑我吗  汤米
Are you laughing at me, Tommy?

583
00:53:27,550 --> 00:53:30,990
就在一切将要走上正轨的时候  亚瑟
Just when things are starting to go right, Arthur...

584
00:53:31,010 --> 00:53:33,120
你竟然做出这种轻生之事
you try and do this.

585
00:53:35,370 --> 00:53:37,810
你不喜欢盛大的派对吗
Don't you like fancy parties?

586
00:53:37,850 --> 00:53:39,380
或者
Or, um...

587
00:53:39,780 --> 00:53:42,710
香槟还有跑车
..Champagne or fast cars?

588
00:53:44,370 --> 00:53:46,300
或者这个怎么样
Or how about this...?

589
00:53:50,920 --> 00:53:53,180
印有你名字的名片
Your name on a business card.

590
00:53:53,200 --> 00:53:54,910
谢尔比
Shelby...

591
00:53:55,530 --> 00:53:57,590
兄弟有限公司
..Brothers Limited.

592
00:53:57,590 --> 00:53:58,980
亚瑟·谢尔比
Arthur Shelby.

593
00:53:59,030 --> 00:54:01,430
赌马公司合伙人
Associate bookmaker.

594
00:54:02,140 --> 00:54:04,830
我今早才从印刷厂取回来
I just had them picked up from the printers this morning.

595
00:54:04,830 --> 00:54:07,660
你是三位合伙人之一
You're one of three shareholders.

596
00:54:08,700 --> 00:54:12,100
你  我还有约翰  根据法律
Me, you and John, and according to the law,

597
00:54:12,100 --> 00:54:13,720
我们是平等合伙人
we are equal partners...

598
00:54:13,720 --> 00:54:16,890
这可都是白纸黑字写着的
and it's written on the paperwork in black and white.

599
00:54:16,960 --> 00:54:20,560
三分之一  三分之一  三分之一
A third, a third, a third.

600
00:54:23,290 --> 00:54:24,820
但是
But the thing is...

601
00:54:24,820 --> 00:54:28,190
我和约翰也很愿意平分你的股份
well, me and John quite fancy splitting your share so,

602
00:54:28,190 --> 00:54:32,040
所以下一次记得用枪
just next time, use a gun, man.

603
00:54:35,820 --> 00:54:39,490
我们在警察局里的人说  那个警长要走了
Our men at the station tell me that copper is leaving town.

604
00:54:40,300 --> 00:54:42,280
我们没事了
We're in the clear.

605
00:54:44,850 --> 00:54:47,450
我们正在一步一步往上爬  兄弟
We are on our way up in the world, brother.

606
00:54:49,840 --> 00:54:51,580
相信我
Believe me.

